data.value:
Bonds are earned:
• in Ranked Battles (received as a reward at the end of stages and seasons);
• in Grand Battles (a battle type in Random Battles);
• in Random Battles (if teams are composed of Tier X vehicles only).

Sets the size of a displayed indicator depending on the amount of damage received (or blocked). The parameter is calculated based on the percentage ratio of damage received to total hit points of a vehicle. Indicators:
• from 0 to 10%—small;
• from 11 to 30%—medium;
• over 31%—large.
